ZH: 我们必须偿还我们的债务。
EN: We must repay our debts.

ZH: 他答应尽快偿还我的钱。
EN: He promised to repay my money as soon as possible.

ZH: 她通过工作偿还了她的学生贷款。
EN: She repaid her student loan through work.

ZH: 我会按时偿还所有的借款。
EN: I will repay all the loans on time.

ZH: 他决心偿还所有的损失。
EN: He is determined to repay all the losses.

ZH: 我帮助他偿还了他的赌债。
EN: I helped him repay his gambling debts.

ZH: 这笔债务必须偿还在下个月。
EN: This debt must be repaid by next month.

ZH: 她每个月都会偿还一部分贷款。
EN: She repays a portion of the loan every month.

ZH: 我们将逐步偿还我们的负债。
EN: We will gradually repay our debts.

ZH: 我们计划通过卖房产来偿还债务。
EN: We plan to repay the debts by selling the properties.

ZH: 他向银行申请贷款来偿还欠款。
EN: He applied for a loan from the bank to repay the debts.

ZH: 我将用这笔钱偿还我的车贷。
EN: I will use this money to repay my car loan.

ZH: 公司正在努力偿还供应商欠款。
EN: The company is making efforts to repay the debts to suppliers.

ZH: 他每个月都会偿还一定数额的利息。
EN: He repays a certain amount of interest every month.

ZH: 他们希望偿还债务并恢复信用。
EN: They hope to repay the debts and restore their credit.

ZH: 我将为每个人偿还我欠下的债务。
EN: I will repay the debts I owe to everyone.

ZH: 我已经筹集了足够的资金来偿还贷款。
EN: I have raised enough funds to repay the loan.

ZH: 如果你无法偿还贷款，银行可能会采取法律行动。
EN: If you are unable to repay the loan, the bank may take legal action.

ZH: 他为了偿还房贷，每天都在拼命工作。
EN: He works tirelessly every day to repay the mortgage.

ZH: 她借了很多钱，但没有偿还能力。
EN: She borrowed a lot of money, but she has no ability to repay.
